  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large pressure cooker over medium-high heat.",
    "Sear the lamb until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the onion and garlic to the pressure cooker and cook until the onion is translucent, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add the cumin, smoked paprika, salt, and black pepper to the pressure cooker and stir to combine.",
    "Add the rice and water to the pressure cooker, stirring to combine.",
    "Close the lid and cook at high pressure for 15 minutes.",
    "Let the pressure release naturally for 10 minutes, then quick-release any remaining pressure.",
    "Stir in the chopped fresh mint and serve hot."
